Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.06,0:30:15.81,DV 中文,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊…\N{\fn文泉驿微米黑\fs14\1c&H0E95CE&\b1}No, no, no, no, no, no, no! No! No! No!
